It was created before I started out

665
00:43:38,781 --> 00:43:41,623
on my research and development project, and you can tell.

666
00:43:43,184 --> 00:43:45,685
White paths are the generic play styles.

667
00:43:45,925 --> 00:43:48,507
In the middle, we have the combat one, and above,

