00:46:19,330 --> 00:46:21,372
The new section actually looks bigger than it is here.

700
00:46:21,772 --> 00:46:23,894
It's effectively one room and two corridors,

701
00:46:24,094 --> 00:46:27,277
plus the branch, so again, relatively low cost.

